85
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,599
Can we talk later?

86
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,360
Of course, dear.

87
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:43,959
We can talk later.

88
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,040
Thank you.

89
00:13:05,439 --> 00:13:07,079
I'll go talk to her.

90
00:13:56,439 --> 00:13:58,240
