114
00:16:19,479 --> 00:16:22,000
-Stop that cutesy voice too.
-Why?

115
00:16:22,079 --> 00:16:24,599
-Don't bump your head against mine.
-But I want to.

116
00:16:24,680 --> 00:16:27,199
