122
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,880
Hey, Sun.

123
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:45,920
-Hey.
-Hey.

124
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:46,839
Eat with us.

125
00:16:46,920 --> 00:16:49,240
Sit down. Take a seat.

126
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:58,959
